BitOTTer Perl Tools: 
BitOTTer Market Data Tool for MPEx -- v0.01 alpha 
	-- Will connect to IRC and allow botcontroller to issue DEPTH|VWAP commands to mpexbot 
	-- parsed output prints to terminal window where script is launched (STDOUT).
BitOTTer Depth Tool for MPEx (bitotter_depth.pl) -- v0.02 : Support for mpexbot
BitOTTer VWAP Tool for MPEx [Volume Weighted Average Price] (bitotter_vwap.pl) -- v0.02 : Support for mpexbot
BitOTTer (bitotter.pl)  -- deprecated for now

