BitOTTer VWAP Tool for MPEx [Volume Weighted Average Price] (bitotter_vwap.pl) v0.02
This tool will display the rolling VWAP per MPSIC in 1/7/30 day format 
from pastebin URL via mpexbot.

Usage: ./bitotter_vwap.pl <pastebin-raw-url> <MPSIC> [usetor|no-tor]
Output Sample:
~$ ./bitotter_vwap.pl http://pastebin.com/raw.php?i=SoMeKeYId S.MPOE usetor
TOR ENABLED - Connecting to pastebin via Tor Socket...
..::[ BitOTTer VWAP Tool for MPEx: S.MPOE ]::..
S.MPOE:
	1d avg: => 73051.3497931
	1d min: => 71102
	1d max: => 76717
	1d vsh: => 72966
	1d vsa: => 5330264789
	1d cnt: => 18

	7d avg: => 74601.5589027
	7d min: => 67600
	7d max: => 76718
	7d vsh: => 514764
	7d vsa: => 38402196867
	7d cnt: => 38

	30d avg: => 69740.4746779
	30d min: => 61614
	30d max: => 78628
	30d vsh: => 42106894
	30d vsa: => 2936554774774
	30d cnt: => 3361

